snippet.title: Cadence of Hyrule - Crypt of the NecroDancer Featuring The Legend of Zelda - Season Pass
snippet.description:
Keep stepping to the beat with new content for Cadence of Hyrule – Crypt of the NecroDancer Featuring The Legend of Zelda!

The Season Pass and DLC Pack 1 will be available today with DLC Pack 2 & 3 releasing before the end of October. A physical version including all the DLC Packs will released on Oct. 23rd!

https://cadenceofhyrule.nintendo.com

#CadenceofHyrule, NintendoSwitch, #Zelda
